commit.title: [engine] Remove and deprecate `nf_enter` et al.
commit.message:
[engine] Remove and deprecate `nf_enter` et al.

After the introduction of `EConstr`, normalization should have become
unnecessary, we thus deprecate the `nf_*` family of functions.

Test-suite passes, however full CI conformance requires a fix to be
done in the next commit.
